@startuml
title Resolver Stage - Class Diagram (Current)
set namespaceSeparator none
left to right direction
hide empty members
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #f7e9dc
  BorderColor #d9c2a8
}

class PlanningPipeline {
  - _resolve_stage: ResolveStage
  - _pending_expiry: IPendingExpiryService
  + open(...): Iterator[Iterable[TransformResult]]
}

class ResolveUseCase {
  + iter_resolved(...): Iterable[TransformResult]
  + run(...): CommandResult
  - _iter_resolved(...): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class PlanningPipelineHooks {
  - _pending_expiry: IPendingExpiryService
  + plan_hooks(): PipelineHooks
}

class PipelineOrchestrator {
  + run(source): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class ResolveContextStage {
  - _batch_index: IBatchIndexService
  - _resolver: ResolveProcessor
  + run(source): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class ResolveStage {
  - resolver: ResolveProcessor
  - catalog: ErrorCatalog
  - _batch_index: IBatchIndexService
  + run(source): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class PipelineRunContext {
  + dedup_store: ISourceDedupStore
  + batch_index: IBatchIndexService
}

class ResolveEngine {
  - dsl: ResolveDsl
  - resolve_rules: ResolveRules
  - link_rules: LinkRules
  - core: ResolveCore
  + __init__(spec, ctx, ..., codec)
  + build_batch_index(matched_rows): dict[str, list[str]]
  + resolve(matched, target_id_map, meta, batch_index)
}

class ResolveCore {
  - resolve_rules: ResolveRules
  - link_rules: LinkRules
  - cache_gateway: ResolveRuntimePort?
  - settings: ResolverSettings
  - catalog: ErrorCatalog
  - sink_spec: SinkSpec?
  - _codec: IPendingCodec
  + build_batch_index(matched_rows): dict[str, list[str]]
  + resolve(matched, target_id_map, meta, batch_index)
  - _resolve_links(...)
  - _validate_sink_mutations(...)
}

class ResolveDsl {
  + compile(spec: ResolveSpec, sink_spec: SinkSpec?): CompiledResolveRules
}

class InMemoryBatchIndexService {
  - _index: dict[str, list[str]]?
  + set_index(index): None
  + get(): dict[str, list[str]]
}

class PendingExpiryService {
  - _cache_gateway: ResolveRuntimePort
  - _settings: ResolverSettings?
  - _last_sweep_at: datetime?
  - _expired: list[PendingLink]
  + sweep(): None
  + drain_expired(): list[PendingLink]
}

class PendingCodecAdapter {
  + serialize(matched, desired_state, meta): str
  + deserialize(pending_rows): PendingLoadResult
}

class IdentityIndexSyncer {
  - runtime: ApplyRuntimePort
  + sync(dataset, resolved_id, key_values): None
}

class ResolveProcessor <<protocol>> {
  + build_batch_index(matched_rows): dict[str, list[str]]
  + resolve(matched, target_id_map, meta, batch_index)
}

class IBatchIndexService <<protocol>> {
  + set_index(index): None
  + get(): dict[str, list[str]]
}

class IPendingExpiryService <<protocol>> {
  + sweep(): None
  + drain_expired(): list[PendingLink]
}

class IPendingCodec <<protocol>> {
  + serialize(...): str
  + deserialize(...): PendingLoadResult
}

class ResolveRuntimePort <<protocol>> {
  + transaction()
  + find_candidates(dataset, identity_key): list[str]
  + add_pending(...): int
  + list_pending_rows(dataset): list[PendingRow]
  + touch_attempt(pending_id): int
  + mark_conflict(pending_id, reason): None
  + mark_resolved_for_source(source_row_id): None
  + sweep_expired(now, reason): list[PendingLink]
  + purge_stale(cutoff, statuses): int
}

class ApplyRuntimePort <<protocol>> {
  + upsert_identity(dataset, identity_key, resolved_id): None
  + list_pending_for_key(dataset, lookup_key): list[PendingLink]
  + mark_resolved(pending_id): None
}

class StageExecutionContext {
  + metadata: PipelineMetadata
  + get(port_type)
  + require(port_type)
}

class ResolverSettings {
  + pending_ttl_seconds: int
  + pending_max_attempts: int
  + pending_sweep_interval_seconds: int
  + pending_on_expire: str
  + pending_allow_partial: bool
  + pending_retention_days: int
}

class ResolveSpec
class ResolveRules
class LinkRules
class SinkSpec
class ErrorCatalog
class MatchedRow
class ResolvedRow
class "TransformResult<T>" as TransformResultT

' Delivery/use-case touchpoints
PlanningPipeline --> ResolveUseCase : resolve pass orchestration
PlanningPipeline --> ResolveStage : injects stage into use-case
PlanningPipeline --> IPendingExpiryService : open().finally drain_expired()
PlanningPipeline ..> ResolveContextStage : pre-resolve checkpoint includes stage pair
PlanningPipelineHooks --> IPendingExpiryService : on_stage_complete("resolve") -> sweep()
ResolveUseCase --> PipelineOrchestrator : [ResolveStage] + hooks per micro-batch
ResolveUseCase --> ResolveStage : execute resolve stage
ResolveUseCase --> ResolveRuntimePort : pending replay + tx scope

' Stage pair and per-run batch index
ResolveContextStage ..> ResolveProcessor : build_batch_index(all_records)
ResolveContextStage --> IBatchIndexService : set_index(index)
ResolveStage --> IBatchIndexService : get() (lazy, once per run)
ResolveStage ..> ResolveProcessor : resolve(..., batch_index)
ResolveStage --> ErrorCatalog : diagnostic_boundary(RESOLVE)
PipelineRunContext o-- IBatchIndexService : shared per-run singleton
PipelineRunContext ..> ResolveContextStage : DI shared state
PipelineRunContext ..> ResolveStage : DI shared state

' Engine / core mechanics
ResolveEngine ..|> ResolveProcessor
ResolveEngine --> ResolveDsl
ResolveEngine --> ResolveCore
ResolveEngine --> StageExecutionContext : compile + extract capabilities
ResolveEngine --> ResolveSpec
ResolveEngine --> IPendingCodec : injected codec
ResolveCore --> ResolveRuntimePort : identity + pending lifecycle ops
ResolveCore --> IPendingCodec : serialize pending payload
ResolveCore --> ResolverSettings
ResolveCore --> ErrorCatalog
ResolveCore --> SinkSpec : validate mutated fields
ResolveCore ..> MatchedRow
ResolveCore ..> ResolvedRow

' Services / ports
InMemoryBatchIndexService ..|> IBatchIndexService
PendingExpiryService ..|> IPendingExpiryService
PendingExpiryService --> ResolveRuntimePort : sweep_expired()
PendingExpiryService --> ResolverSettings : interval guard
PendingCodecAdapter ..|> IPendingCodec
IdentityIndexSyncer --> ApplyRuntimePort : close pending after apply

' Stream types (simplified)
ResolveContextStage ..> TransformResultT : pass-through matched stream
ResolveStage ..> TransformResultT : matched -> resolved stream

' Layout helpers
PlanningPipeline -[hidden]-> ResolveContextStage
ResolveContextStage -[hidden]-> ResolveEngine
ResolveEngine -[hidden]-> ResolveCore
ResolveCore -[hidden]-> ResolveRuntimePort
PlanningPipelineHooks -[hidden]-> PendingExpiryService
IdentityIndexSyncer -[hidden]-> ApplyRuntimePort

note right of ResolveEngine
ResolveEngine is a thin wrapper:
- compiles ResolveSpec via ResolveDsl
- builds ResolveCore
- uses StageExecutionContext for runtime ports/settings/catalog/sink_spec
- shares one instance between ResolveContextStage and ResolveStage (DI)
end note

note right of ResolveUseCase
Resolve mechanics outside ResolveCore:
- pending replay (list_pending_rows + decode)
- micro-batching + transaction scope
- hooks-driven sweep via PlanningPipelineHooks/PendingExpiryService
end note

note bottom of IdentityIndexSyncer
Adjacent layer touchpoint (post-apply / cache refresh):
marks pending rows as resolved after identity index sync.
end note

@enduml
